    "div" : "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-hl7-condition-ver-status-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-hl7-condition-ver-status-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-hl7-condition-ver-status-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 9; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-04-20 16:57:30+0200; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"http://tx.fhir.org/r4\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/condition-ver-status</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 4.0.1\"> version &#x1F4CD;4.0.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><code>unconfirmed</code></td><td>Non confirmé</td><td>There is not sufficient diagnostic and/or clinical evidence to treat this as a confirmed condition.</td></tr><tr><td><code>confirmed</code></td><td>Confirmé</td><td>There is sufficient diagnostic and/or clinical evidence to treat this as a confirmed condition.</td></tr><tr><td><code>refuted</code></td><td>Réfuté</td><td>This condition has been ruled out by diagnostic and clinical evidence.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
